1665
01:35:25.590 --> 01:35:29.310
- It's a question of discipline.
- I'll take you anytime.


1666
01:35:29.470 --> 01:35:31.770
Stop playing the big shot.

1667
01:35:31.930 --> 01:35:33.310
Calm down.

1668
01:35:35.310 --> 01:35:36.520
Stay out of this.

1669
01:35:36.690 --> 01:35:38.480
