a chain reaction.


1687
01:37:00.520 --> 01:37:03.940
Well, what I can do is take...

1688
01:37:04.110 --> 01:37:07.360
...a protective measure
since this is so serious...


1689
01:37:07.530 --> 01:37:10.910
...by suspending Souleymane
for 48 hours.


1690
01:37:11.580 --> 01:37:16.000
That'll give us a little time
to reach a decision.


1691
01:37:18.250 --> 01:37:19.580
Shall we do that?

1692
01:37:20.250 --> 01:37:23.420
However,
I need to see you tomorrow.


1693
01:37:23.590 --> 01:37:26.760
Could you come to my office?

1694
01:37:30.260 --> 01:37:31.300
François.

1695
01:37:33.560 --> 01:37:35.260
I need a word with you.

1696
01:37:36.100 --> 01:37:38.810
