1727
01:39:12.860 --> 01:39:14.360
I'll have spoken out.

1728
01:39:14.990 --> 01:39:17.240
Great, that's a lot of use.

1729
01:39:17.410 --> 01:39:19.490
Do you know what "skank" means?

1730
