2030
02:01:11.850 --> 02:01:12.970
The sperm does?

2031
02:01:13.430 --> 02:01:14.720
No, the baby.

2032
02:01:15.350 --> 02:01:17.390
The human being that's inside.

2033
02:01:17.560 --> 02:01:19.850
- Khoumba?
- Me?


2034
02:01:20.020 --> 02:01:22.230
Yes. That is your name?

2035
02:01:25.820 --> 02:01:27.150
In music...

2036
02:01:27.320 --> 02:01:30.200
...I learned to play the alto recorder...

2037
02:01:30.950 --> 02:01:32.870
...and in Spanish.

2038
