The recorder in Spanish?

2039
02:01:36.750 --> 02:01:39.920
No, in music,
I learned to play the alto recorder.


2040
02:01:40.080 --> 02:01:41.920
And other stuff in Spanish.

2041
02:01:42.090 --> 02:01:45.460
Very good. Can you say
