2044
02:02:01.480 --> 02:02:03.230
I didn't learn anything.

2045
02:02:04.610 --> 02:02:08.990
You can't spend nine months at school
and not learn anything.


2046
02:02:09.360 --> 02:02:11.860
I'm the living proof.

2047
02:02:12.240 --> 02:02:14.870
You got something
from the books we read.


2048
02:02:15.040 --> 02:02:17.080
- Your books are shit.
- They're what?


2049
02:02:17.290 --> 02:02:18.500
They're useless.

2050
02:02:19.790 --> 02:02:22.920
What about a book you read
by yourself?


2051
02:02:24.750 --> 02:02:26.300
The books I read?

2052
02:02:27.010 --> 02:02:29.300
Well, there's The Republic.

2053
02:02:29.880 --> 02:02:31.590
The book The Republic.

2054
02:02:33.550 --> 02:02:34.760
By Plato?

2055
